I don't know when you tried to use the CVS version, but it should be
stable now (at least it should compile), which was maybe not the case 2
or 3 days ago.

It would be great if you can try the CVS again, and send me an error
report if you still have problems.

> On Wed, 2006-02-22 at 13:39 +0100, Nicolas Boichat wrote:
